magnesium chloride powder on a approx. 10 mug/cm**2
carbon stripping foil, and by adding an ultra thin Au
layer on top for protection and charge/solid angle
The detection system consisted of four Si
surface barrier detectors, thickness of 1000 mum
Correction for the abundance of Mg-24 in natural Mg
between the different detectors did not exceed 1.2%
factor was undoubtedly related to the integrated number

reactions on 24Mg. This uncertainty, when the
